  <div class="container">
    <p class="kicker">03 / About</p>
    <h2 id="about-heading">About</h2>
    <div class="about-body">
      <p>
        I’m an engineer in Toronto who’s spent a career where spreadsheets meet heavy machinery —
        analyzing fleets, auditing thirty thousand contracts, and running cost control on $160M of
        construction, including two grid-scale battery storage projects.
      </p>
      <p>
        Somewhere along the way I started automating the boring parts, and never stopped. These
        days I build web apps end-to-end: design, code, deploy. I like tools that do their job
        without asking for an account, systems that run themselves, and shipping something real
        over polishing something imaginary.
      </p>
      <p class="closing">
        This site doubles as my own ledger — a running record of what I’ve built.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

